folder: Grand Central Parkway & 78th Avenue, Queens, NY
text:
Grand Central Parkway, south from 78th Avenue, showing the Parkway passing under the Independent Subway bridge and the Union Turnpike bridge. This area is a point of juncture for several of the boroughs principal highways.

P. L. Sperr

View 1: February 10, 1937
View 2: April 23, 1936
